description._content: Description: Office Curator, Botanic Station, Seychelles. Location: Seychelles Date: 1900-1929 Description: Part of Botanic Station, shewing boulders which have to be removed. Location: Seychelles Date: 1900-1929 Description: Part of Botanic Station, Seychelles, shewing, in the foreground, many recently planted trees. Location: Seychelles Date: 1900-1929 Description: Stream passing through Botanic Station.
